{
  "stem": "1568.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At least I'm here in America.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why don't you come to America?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So there was-- being still a minor, I was able to register as an orphan, and it took me two weeks and I was in the United States.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I came to New York with a bunch of other kids.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And again, like any other thing, come to New York they ask, where do you want to go?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The idea was to get the people out of New York as much as possible, so they move them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, I don't know, but I have a friend in Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "His name is Morris Pearl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, I don't remember what the organization was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was an international organization, not a Jewish organization, that sent me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I guess they got in contact with Vista Del Mar here, which I was sent to Los Angeles, went to Morris Pearl because he had an apartment, but the next day got in contact from Vista Del Mar by a social worker.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her name was Anna [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Schaefer. ?] Still alive, and I still keep contact with her until today.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She's invited to all my affairs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And basically, they took me under jurisdiction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did not live on the premises of Vista Del Mar, but they were under jurisdiction.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They ask me, what do you want to do?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Send you to school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Again, I had five years of schooling at home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I knew, and I was being impressed at home, that schooling is important.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You went to cheder, you [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was not driven in-- into my mind, from-- from where I come that-- how important knowledge and education is.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
